Constancio Says Contagion Plays Crucial Role in Worsening Crisis

-- B y   E l i s a   M a r t i n u z z i
-- 
2011-10-10T08:01:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/constancio-says-contagion-plays-crucial-role-in-worsening-crisis.html
European Central Bank Vice President
 Vitor Constancio  said contagion has played a “crucial role” in
exacerbating the region’s fiscal crisis.  Constancio made the comments in a speech in Milan today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisa Martinuzzi in Milan at 
